headline: GTA Online
subtitle: The Weeny Issi Rally SUV Returns This Week
content:
The Weeny Issi Rally (SUV) is on pace to become Los Santos’ most beloved British import.

This SUV returns to the Southern San Andreas Super Autos website and Simeon’s Premium Deluxe Motorsport showroom for a limited time this week.

Plus, spread your car collection out across five spacious floors in the multi-floor garage, which is available at 30% off this week from the Dynasty 8 in-game website.
